casebody.data:
Dennis E. YARRELL
v.
BEAUFORT COUNTY SUPERIOR COURT. No. 254P03-2. Supreme Court of North Carolina. January 25, 2007. Dennis E. Yarrell, Pro Se. John G. Barnwell, Assistant Attorney General, for Beaufort Superior Court.

ORDER

Upon consideration of the petition filed by Plaintiff on the 8th day of January 2007 in this matter for a writ of certiorari to review the order of the North Carolina Court of Appeals, the following order was entered and is hereby certified to the North Carolina Court of Appeals:

"Denied by order of the Court in conference, this the 25th day of January 2007."
